<p>Friday 3.8.17<br/>Losing our new Sgt who is going to Officers school, am again only N.C.O. left on bearer section, any amount of work  Walked to Recquotoile at night where a number of the Portuguese are billeted, met one who could speak English well, was very interesting to talk to.</p>
<p>Saturday 4.8.17<br/>Sent home full volume (8 copies) of "Australia in the great war"</p>
<p>Sunday 5.8.17<br/>Went to Church service in a little barn at night.  Very little doing during the day.</p>
<p>Monday 6.8.17<br/>Granted a days leave to St Omer &amp; had a good day, rode to &amp; fro on bike.  Had a yarn to a couple of Scotch lassies from</p>
